{"problem_id": 11354, "annotation": "xiaokaizhang_2023-03-06", "source": "GeoQA-area-11758", "problem_level": 1, "problem_text_cn": "如图，在△ABC中，AD是BC边上的高线，CE是AB边上的中线，若CD＝AD＝2，则△DCE的面积是（）", "problem_text_en": "", "problem_img": "11354.png", "construction_cdl": ["Polygon()", "Collinear()", "Cocircular()"], "text_cdl": [], "image_cdl": [], "goal_cdl": "", "problem_answer": "", "theorem_seqs": [], "raw_choices": ["4", "3", "2", "l"], "raw_answer": "如图，过E点作EH⊥BC于H，∵EH⊥BC，AD⊥BC，∴EH∥AD，∴△BHE∽△BDA，∴\\frac{BE}{AB}=\\frac{EH}{AD}，∵BE＝0.5×AB，AD＝2，∴EH＝0.5×2＝1，∴S△DCE＝0.5×CD×EH=0.5×2×1=1．故选：D．", "raw_label": 4, "raw_formal_point": ["三角形的面积"], "raw_comment": "本题考查了相似三角形的判定与性质，三角形的面积计算公式，利用相似三角形的性质求出EH的长是解题的关键．"}